# Rules

These rules are broken down into categories.

- Documentation
- CI/CD
- Project Structure

## Documentation

- When documenting
  - ensure to provide citations in `.aim/todo/docs/citations/README.md` for any factual claims or technical details.
  - every todo item in `.aim/todo/docs/` requires a `meta.json` with the `id` value.
    - This value is used to track related documents across the project.
